msgid "!play"
msgstr "·"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_soltys.html.heex:86
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"\"Soltys\" means \"Mayor\" (village head) in Polish. The game is a cult "
"classic in Poland, celebrated for its depiction of mid-1990s village life "
"and folk humor."
msgstr ""
"\"Soltys\"는 폴란드어 \"Mayor\"(빌리지 헤드)를 의미합니다. 이 게임은 폴란드의 경전 클래식이며, 1990 년대 중반 "
"마을 생활과 민간 유머의 묘사를 축하했습니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm.html.heex:50
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"(1992) — Revolution Software's debut. Medieval fantasy with innovative "
"Virtual Theatre AI system."
msgstr ""
"(1992) — 혁명 소프트웨어의 데뷔. 혁신적인 Virtual Theatre AI 시스템을 갖춘 Medieval Fantasy."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm.html.heex:14
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"(1994) — Cyberpunk masterpiece by Revolution Software. Full CD version with "
"voice acting."
msgstr "(1994) - 혁명 소프트웨어에 의해 Cyberpunk 걸작. 음성 연기를 가진 가득 차있는 CD 버전."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm.html.heex:32
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"(1994) — Dark cyberpunk top-down adventure by Creative Reality. Full CD "
"version with voice acting."
msgstr "(1994) - 크리에이티브 리얼리티의 다크 사이버펑크 탑다운 모험. 음성 연기를 가진 가득 차있는 CD 버전."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm.html.heex:41
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"(1995) — Comic Indiana Jones-style adventure in the Amazon. Full CD version "
"with voice acting."
msgstr "(1995) - 아마존의 Comic Indiana Jones-style 모험. 음성 연기를 가진 가득 차있는 CD 버전."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm.html.heex:59
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"(1995) — Surreal Polish puzzle adventure by LK Avalon. Rescue your "
"grandfather from underground pirates."
msgstr "(1995) — LK Avalon의 Surreal 폴란드어 퍼즐 모험. 지하 해적에서 할아버지를 구출하십시오."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm.html.heex:23
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"(1996) — Hilarious Spanish point & click parody of Dracula. Full version "
"with MP3 voice acting."
msgstr ""
"(1996) - Hilarious 스페인어 포인트 및 Dracula의 패러디를 클릭합니다. MP3 음성 행동을 가진 가득 차있는 버전."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:122
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"(ECWolf compiled to WebAssembly via Emscripten). DOOM games are powered by"
msgstr "(Emscripten을 통해 WebAssembly에 컴파일된 ECWolf). DOOM 게임에 의해 구동"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:117
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"(GoldSource reimplementation compiled to WebAssembly). Wolfenstein 3D is "
"powered by"
msgstr ""
"(GoldSource Reimplementation은 WebAssembly에 컴파일되었습니다). Wolfenstein 3D에 의해 구동 "
"됩니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:127
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "(PrBoom+ compiled to WebAssembly). Quake games are powered by"
msgstr "(PrBoom+ WebAssembly에 컴파일). Quake 게임에 의해 구동"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:129
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "(QuakeSpasm compiled to WebAssembly). Quake II is powered by"
msgstr "(QuakeSpasm는 WebAssembly에 컴파일했습니다). Quake II에 의해 구동 됩니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:131
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"(Yamagi Quake II compiled to WebAssembly). All support keyboard, mouse, and "
"gamepad input."
msgstr "(Yamagi Quake II는 WebAssembly에 컴파일). 모든 지원 키보드, 쥐 및 gamepad 입력."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:16
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ") to play."
msgstr ") 놀이."

