#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake2.html.heex:82
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Quake II was originally going to be called \"Wor\" — id couldn't secure the "
"trademark, so they reused the Quake name despite having a completely "
"different setting and story."
msgstr ""
"Quake II는 원래 \"Wor\"라고 부르려고했습니다 - id는 상표를 확보 할 수 없었다, 그래서 그들은 완전히 다른 설정과 "
"이야기에도 불구하고 Quake 이름을 재사용."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:108
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake2.html.heex:12
