#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake_shareware.html.heex:92
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Quake's soundtrack was composed by Trent Reznor of Nine Inch Nails — the "
"nail ammunition boxes feature the NIN logo as a tribute."
msgstr ""
"Quake의 soundtrack는 Nine Inch Nails의 Trent Reznor에 의해 구성되었습니다. - 네일 "
"ammunition 상자는 NIN 로고를 tribute로 특징으로합니다."

