msgstr "— 단계 2 수준은 일반적으로 더 큰 옥외 지역과 더불어 단계 1 보다는 더 여깁니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_doom.html.heex:72
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— PrBoom+ compiled to WebAssembly via Emscripten (GPL-2.0). Supports WADs, "
"PWADs, DEH/BEX patches, OPL synthesis, gamepad input, and widescreen "
"rendering."
msgstr ""
"- Emscripten (GPL-2.0)을 통해 WebAssembly에 컴파일된 PrBoom+. 지원 WADs, PWADs, "
"DEH/BEX 패치, OPL 합성, 게임 패드 입력 및 와이드 스크린 렌더링."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_freedoom1.html.heex:83
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Press Tab in maze-like sections to keep your bearings."
msgstr "— 당신의 방위를 지키는 maze 같이 단면도에 있는 탭을 누르십시오."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_halflife_uplink.html.heex:38
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Primary fire"
msgstr "- 1차 화재"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein.html.heex:54
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Push walls hide treasure rooms and secret levels. Systematically check "
"textured walls by pressing Space."
msgstr "— 푸시 벽은 보물 방과 비밀 수준을 숨깁니다. Systematically 우주를 눌러 질감 벽을 확인합니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake.html.heex:79
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Quake is full of secrets. Look for shootable walls, hidden platforms, and "
"underwater passages."
msgstr "— Quake는 비밀이 가득합니다. 촬영 가능한 벽, 숨겨진 플랫폼 및 수중 통행을 찾습니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_librequake.html.heex:69
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Quake mods spanning over two decades are compatible with LibreQuake."
msgstr ""
"— Quake mods spanning over two decades are compatible with LibreQuake."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake.html.heex:32
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— QuakeSpasm compiled to WebAssembly via Emscripten. Features dual WebGL + "
"software rendering, QuakeC mod support, and in-browser save games."
msgstr ""
"— QuakeSpasm은 Emscripten을 통해 WebAssembly에 컴파일되었습니다. 특징 이중 WebGL + 소프트웨어 렌더링,"
" QuakeC mod 지원, 및 브라우저 저장 게임."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_bass.html.heex:86
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Read item descriptions for entertaining commentary. The humor is subtle "
"and dry."
msgstr "— 재미있는 논평에 대한 항목 설명 읽기. 유머는 미묘하고 건조합니다."

